ZH: 我已经吃了一半蛋糕。
EN: I have already eaten half of the cake.

ZH: 他们打了一半篮球比赛。
EN: They played half of the basketball game.

ZH: 我们只走了一半的路程。
EN: We have only walked half of the distance.

ZH: 她一半时间在学习中度过。
EN: She spends half of her time studying.

ZH: 这部电影只看了一半。
EN: I only watched half of this movie.

ZH: 我的朋友们一半都住在这个城市。
EN: Half of my friends live in this city.

ZH: 餐厅里的饭菜都吃了一半。
EN: I only ate half of the food in the restaurant.

ZH: 班里一半的学生会参加音乐会。
EN: Half of the students in the class will attend the concert.

ZH: 这个问题我只解答了一半。
EN: I have only answered half of the question.

ZH: 他们的房子很大，但只用了一半。
EN: Their house is big, but only half of it is used.

ZH: 这个杯子里的水只喝了一半。
EN: I only drank half of the water in this cup.

ZH: 昨天的工作我只完成了一半。
EN: I only completed half of yesterday's work.

ZH: 我的家人半数在中国，半数在美国。
EN: Half of my family is in China, and the other half is in the US.

ZH: 他的钱花了一半在旅行上。
EN: He spent half of his money on traveling.

ZH: 运动员们只完成了比赛的一半。
EN: The athletes only completed half of the competition.

ZH: 这篇文章写了一半，还需要编辑。
EN: I have written half of this article, it still needs editing.

ZH: 食物一半在冰箱里保存。
EN: Half of the food is stored in the refrigerator.

ZH: 这个城市一半的人口住在郊区。
EN: Half of the city's population lives in the suburbs.

ZH: 这张沙发只占了客厅的一半。
EN: This sofa only takes up half of the living room.

ZH: 这个游戏只进行了一半。
EN: The game is only halfway done.
